_sText: The screen shots are really dark, but when you are ingame its much lighter and you can see really well, its a really fun map, rated really good in beta ingame stages, by random people. basicly the ct's try running up the hill, theres max 4 t's, and around 30 ct's, they t's get machine guns mp5's and awps and nades, the ct's get 2 smokes, and ump45's, mp5, and mac10. if you like this map come play at 8.9.4.237:27015 thats our css server, before we submit a new map to this site we always test it on our server and see if people like it! our site is www.teamramrod.tk!
